<section class="about">
    <div class="about-inner">
        <h2 class="about-title">The people behind the shine</h2>
        <div class="about-text">
            <p class="about-description">
                We're an independent studio working with clients across the world. We specialize in building websites the right way, thinking holistically about the product, with obsessive attention to craft and detail. We've partnered with brands across industries, and we're always looking for the next challenge.
            </p>
            <p class="about-founders">
                Founded by designers and developers who believe great work comes from trust, honesty, and caring about the details that make the difference.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .about {
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        padding: 6rem 2rem;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .about-inner {
        max-width: 70rem;
        width: 100%;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 4rem;
        align-items: start;
    }

    .about-title {
        font-family: var(--font-titles);
        font-weight: 100;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
        line-height: 1.1;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .about-text {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .about-description {
        opacity: 0.7;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .about-founders {
        opacity: 0.5;
        line-height: 1.6;
        font-size: 1rem;
        margin: 0;
        font-style: italic;
    }

    @media (max-width: 48rem) {
        .about-inner {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 2rem;
        }
    }
</style>
